                          <!-- @Calculated /AUTOSAR/TOP-LEVEL-PACKAGES/TI_F29H85x/ELEMENTS/Cdd_Xbar/CddXbarConfiguration/CddXbarOutputXbarConfig/CddXbarOutputXbarInstanceConfig/CddXbarOutputXbarInstanceConfig/CddXbarOutputXbarInput: MAX(XPath: count(ecu:list(&apos;Output_Xbar_InputGroups&apos;)))-->
